headline: Principal Financial: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The Des Moines, Iowa-based company said it had profit of $3.92 per share. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring gains, came to $1.94 per share. The results did not meet Wall Street expectations.

headline: Principal Financial Group Announces Full Year and Fourth Quarter 2024 Results as well as 2025 Outlook
summary: DES MOINES, Iowa, February 06, 2025--Principal Financial Group® (Nasdaq: PFG) announced results for full year and fourth quarter 2024.
